reviewText: THIS IS A GREAT MOVIE FOR YOUNGER CHILDREN FROM 2 TO 10 OR THERE ABOUTS. IT TEACHES GOOD MORALS AND BEHAVIOR. MY KIDS LOVE THE ACTION AND STORY LINE, WHILE I LOVE THE UNDERLYING MESSAGE. KINDNESS, FORGIVENESS, LOVE. I  RECOMMEND ANY OF THE ADVENTURES IN ODYSSEY MOVIES TO ANY PARENT WHO CARES  WHAT THEIR CHILDREN ARE SWALLOWING THESE DAYS.
